This directory tree have the version 0.1 of Caldo.

Caldo is a fast and free BitTorrent search engine and client.

This program can have bugs, if you find one, report it at
https://github.com/Azag/Caldo or to my e-mail (rmasad [at] gmail.com).

If you have any idea to make better Caldo send it to my e-mail
(rmasad [at] gmail.com).

To install it, the dependency are:
  * python >= 2.5
  * python-qt4 (PyQt4)

